  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 400 degrees Fahrenheit.",
    "Season the chicken breast with salt and pepper.",
    "Bake the chicken in the oven for 20 minutes or until it reaches 165 degrees Fahrenheit.",
    "Let the chicken rest for 5 minutes before slicing it thinly.",
    "In a small bowl, whisk together the mayonnaise and sriracha.",
    "Spread the mayonnaise mixture on the baguette.",
    "Add the sliced chicken, pickled carrots, pickled daikon, cucumber, and cilantro on the baguette.",
    "Drizzle the deglaze fond over the top of the sandwich.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy."
